Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the organization learned that\NShinichi and Conan were the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone close to me would be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who knows\Nthe truth is Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hide my identity yet again today,\Nin which there is only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bizarre Manhunt Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robberies, kidnappings, murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no end to these crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why your detective\Nskills are proving so useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man Kogoro gets\Nall the credit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done! These are my special\NCriminal Pursuit Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I use these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try pressing the button on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll display the location of this\Ntransmitter within a 20-kilometer radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep it here most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a sticker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Masami Hirota!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Find my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father, who works away from home\Nin Tokyo, quit his taxi driver job,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's been missing\Nfor a full month now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you've come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took time off from school in\NYamagata to come look for him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can\Nturn to now, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I'll take on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my father, Kenzo Hirota.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's 5'9" and 48 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my father's cat. Its name is Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has three others\Nnamed Tei, Gou, and Ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding people isn't really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he had one of these on him,\NI could've found him in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll stick it on Ran\Nand test it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The transmitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I stuck it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother died when I was little,\Nso my father is my only family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything were to happen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Well, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't found any leads...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masami-san again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the third time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he didn't\Nsocialize much with other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he almost never talked about himself,\Naccording to his coworkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goukai Teiou pulls ahead of the pack\Nto earn his 5th G-1 victory in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goukai Teiou? (Heroic Emperor)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my father's cat. Its name is Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has three others\Nnamed Tei, Gou, and Ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai, Tei, Gou, and Ou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rearrange them and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Goukai Teiou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goukai Teiou truly is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirota-san loves horse races!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he named his cats\Nafter a famous horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you can find him\Nat the race track!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is my first time\Nat a race track!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and find Masami-san's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! Like he'd\Nbe that easy to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mocking us detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! I'm such a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He's purposely gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to scare him away\Nand then lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll follow him back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't something seem\Ndifferent about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wearing more grown-up clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it looks like she has makeup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't seen her dad in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she'd wear make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That case was as easy as pie\Nin the hands of Kogoro Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found him after he hanged\Nhimself last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Hirota-san's daughter?\NThe one who came looking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So there was\Nsomething going after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wasn't right about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd pay me a full\Nyears' worth of rent all at once
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I let him have an apartment\Nwith no questions asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus all the bills\Nwere brand new and crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is if his daughter did come over,\Nthen she's probably dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I thought\NHirota-san committed suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police said it was a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hung from the ceiling\Nafter he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the large hand marks\Non the victim's neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the murderer must have\Nbeen quite a large man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These were lying on the floor\Nnear the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Masami-san's glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her body hasn't turned up yet,\Nbut I'm pretty sure that she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. Don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Masami-san might've been murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she just found her father, too!\NHow horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know for sure\Nthat she was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now what? If only\Nwe had a clue to go by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I accidentally\Nput the transmitter on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that it's moving means\NMasami-san might still be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pachinko parlor?!\NWhat's Masami-san doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the battery's dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find her quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no kids allowed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Why were you gone so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like that for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must really be\Nworried about Masami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's weird about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been looking\Nup here this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who was hanging out\Nby Hirota-san's apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think about it,\Nthe killer was a large man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed Masami-san's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right here! I'll go catch him\Nand find out where Masami-san is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Masami-san?\NWhat's happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What great luck! Who'd have thought\Nthe killer would come to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killer?! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! Then who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a detective too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I, too, was\Nasked to find Hirota-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really a detective, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That young woman came after me,\Nso I instinctually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been sort of a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wear these sunglasses\Nso people can't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your stupid excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious!\NMasami-san's life is at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were asked to locate\NKenzo Hirota-san as well, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:11:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But there was something\Nstrange about his family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the man who hired me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to find his brother\Nwho left Kyushu for Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said his brother\Nwas his only relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His only relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masami-san was supposed to be\NHirota-san's only relative!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird, too! Masami-san's father\Ncame here from Yamagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can't be two Hirota-sans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one other thing that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this from the taxi company\Nthat Hirota-san worked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he would drive\Nthe same route every single evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without bothering to\Npick up any passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he would do this\Nat breakneck speeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just letting off steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happens all the time to middle-aged men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is this client of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Hirota. 28 years old. He's a\Nlarge man, over 6 feet 3 inches tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he be the large man\Nthe inspector was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Did you tell this man\Nanything about Hirota-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it was after that\Nthat Hirota-san was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wondered if there\Nwas any connection...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! This man murdered Hirota-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he took Masami-san with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How can I contact him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He contacts me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have any clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake! It's the man\NI ran into at the pachinko parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did the transmitter on\NMasami-san's watch lead me there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really is the killer,\Nand he was wearing Masami-san's watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then she's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...been murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and recharge it, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop rushing me! Being impatient\Nisn't going to help you any!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you remember the\Nrobbery from the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one where they stole a billion yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the one with the trio of thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A security guard was killed\Nwhen he recklessly tried to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he got\Nfor taking them lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm, cool, and collected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your style, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really in this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely! I saw him go in\Non my way home from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange! The transmitter\Nhasn't moved at all for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't take the watch off\Nand escape, did he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's staying in Room 802.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought he was really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I'm in a hurry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sweet smell...\Nit's potassium cyanide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He couldn't live with\Nwhat he had done so he killed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Masami-san's watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he did take it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty duralumin cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two separate, yet conflicting\Nrequests to find the same person...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzo Hirota-san acting strange\Nand driving the same route everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then these cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hirota-san was single?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He didn't have any daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he was born and raised in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I have this case figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These empty cases are the key\Nto unlocking this mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masami-san, Kenzo Hirota,\Nand Akira Hirota...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know they're not relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they have no connection whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the context of\Nthe other recent incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire mystery comes unraveled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the three thieves\Nwho stole the one billion in yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the number of cases here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they must have been filled\Nwith the stolen money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then the reason Hirota-san\Nsped down the same route every day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to rehearse their getaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their plan succeeded, but he took\Nall the money for himself and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He betrayed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eager to catch Hirota-san,\Nthe two partners concocted lies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent separate detectives\Nto locate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then when he was found,\Nhe was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killed by the large man,\Nwho was then killed in this very room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killed by the woman who claimed\Nshe was Hirota-san's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she was the mastermind\Nbehind these murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hairstyle and overall\Nappearance were different,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but her build and the number\Nof suitcases she had weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Masami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! No cutting in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dad's gonna be chopped into pieces\Nand buried alive in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we don't hurry and save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go right ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow that taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason she seemed different\Nthe second time we saw her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was because when we found Hirota-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was in a hurry and hadn't\Ncompleted her disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Hirota-san's reaction\Nwhen he saw her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't because he was\Nsurprised to see his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because he was terrified\Nof the partners he betrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,coming to exact revenge on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why didn't\NI realize it sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now? We lost her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 100% certain she\Nentered this harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely somewhere nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the money, Masami Hirota?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, Akemi Miyano-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okita-san! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sleeping drug you gave me\Nto put him to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant he drank it, he fell\Nto the ground and stopped moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he had in brute strength\Nhe lacked in intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that he\Nwould alert the authorities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by throwing all his money\Naround the instant he got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as someone that\Ndangerous remained alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my own plans would be hindered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intended to kill everyone\Nfrom the start, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hand over the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't here! It's being\Nheld at a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of you using me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm through with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think that is an option?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I escape overseas,\NI'll let you know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:19:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that, now. As long as\Nyou're alive, my plan is in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're dead, all links\Nto me will have vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily find any number of\Nreplacements for you and the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting my own hands dirty\Ngoes against my principles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it will be the finishing touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me and you'll never\Nknow where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a pretty good idea\Nwhere to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job. Allow me to\Nexpress my gratitude by killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the boy from\Nthe detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My transmitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met at the agency,\NI accidentally stuck it on your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After following the signal, I arrived\Nat the hotel and then ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you with all the large suitcases,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized you were leaving\Nwith the billion yen that you stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea there was\Nanything on the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the watch belonged\Nto that big man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he broke his own watch when he\Nlost control and killed Hirota-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I gave him mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy intended to kill everyone\Nfrom the very start, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirota-san realized this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he betrayed us before\Nwe knew what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean this man is the mastermind\Nbehind the billion-yen robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Okita scouted for\Npeople he needed to realize his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would put these people into teams\Nand have them commit robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor had it that he would eliminate\Nhis recruits to keep them silent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after they would finish his jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't know it was the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you where the suitcases\Nwith the one billion yen are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front desk of the hotel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you got in the taxi,\Nyou didn't have the suitcases with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply assumed that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss behind\Nthe billion yen robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as she had said, the billion yen\Nwas being kept at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bill codes matched\Nthose of the stolen money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the billion-yen\Nrobbery case came to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:47.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:56.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:05.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:10.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:17.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:27.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:34.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:40.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:50.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:55.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up there!
